                                </span></div></div></div> <!----></div> <div class="info mt-3"><div class="info__article-img"><div data-v-10f10a3e><img data-srcset="https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/954440f6bb547bd74a9a4f8de7d73ee1.png 480w,https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/954440f6bb547bd74a9a4f8de7d73ee1.png 960w,https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/954440f6bb547bd74a9a4f8de7d73ee1.png 1920w,https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/954440f6bb547bd74a9a4f8de7d73ee1.png 2500w" alt="Fostering Multidisciplinary Collaboration in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Education: Tutorial Based on the AI-READI Bootcamp" title="Fostering Multidisciplinary Collaboration in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Education: Tutorial Based on the AI-READI Bootcamp" aria-label="Article Thumbnail Image" src="https://asset.jmir.pub/placeholder.svg" data-v-10f10a3e></div> <button data-test="article-img-info" aria-label="Open modal window to view the image" class="info__article-img-info"><span aria-hidden="true" class="icon fas fa-search-plus"></span></button></div> <div class="info__title-authors"><h1 tabindex="0" aria-label="Fostering Multidisciplinary Collaboration in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Education: Tutorial Based on the AI-READI Bootcamp" class="h3 mb-0 mt-0">Fostering Multidisciplinary Collaboration in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Education: Tutorial Based on the AI-READI Bootcamp</h1> <h2 class="info__hidden-title">
